What do you think of our list?

00:04:47.980 --> 00:04:50.370
Know of any other actors who lied to get roles?

00:04:50.370 --> 00:04:55.180
Tell us about them in the comments, and subscribe
to our YouTube channel for more videos.

00:04:55.180 --> 00:04:55.629
Thanks for watching.

